    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔投资者因担心选举后“混乱”而撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ecuador-bond-investors-retreat-for-fear-of-post-election-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几周前，投资者纷纷购买厄瓜多尔的美元债券，因为他们看到民意调查显示，亲市场的现任总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚 (Daniel Noboa) 将在第一轮选举中获胜。随后，路易莎·冈萨雷斯 (Luisa González) 胜出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ecuador-bond-investors-retreat-for-fear-of-post-election-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 13:57:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税成为焦点，金价有望再创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/gold-xauusd-holds-near-2-900-as-traders-weigh-trade-fears-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令其政府考虑对众多贸易伙伴征收对等关税，导致美元走低，金价上涨至另一个历史高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/gold-xauusd-holds-near-2-900-as-traders-weigh-trade-fears-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 00:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元下跌，因美国暂缓立即征收关税：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统决定征收对等关税（但不是立即征收）后，股市扩大涨幅，而债券收益率与美元一起下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资产激增，最大 CLO ETF 规模突破 200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/biggest-clo-etf-pushes-past-20-billion-in-assets-on-2025-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的跟踪抵押贷款债务的交易所交易基金在推出后不到五年的时间里，其资产规模首次超过 200 亿美元，主要受寻求浮动利率的投资者的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/biggest-clo-etf-pushes-past-20-billion-in-assets-on-2025-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:56:46 GMT</pubDate>
